Modifications introduced in this distribution
---------------------------------------------
- The upstream source tree was vendored into `SeedVR/` with binary
  checkpoints, `.git/`, `__pycache__/`, and pre-built wheels removed.
- A thin Python wrapper (`runtime.py`) was added to load the model once
  and process per-clip numpy buffers in memory.
- A pure-function temporal blending utility (`temporal_blend.py`) was
  added to combine refined frames with the upstream FlowWAM output.
- No source file under `SeedVR/` has been modified.
